about:
We have over 25 years of accounting experience and can handle anything from data entry, bank reconciliations, journal entries, inventory valuations, depreciation schedules, accounts payable, accounts receivable, adjusting journal entries to financial statements. We can help you with  your month-end and/or year-end closing procedures. We are Quickbooks and Quickbooks Point of Sale experts, and have experience in many other accounting softwares including Timberline, MAS 90, PC Advisor, American Contractor, Micros/Aloha and Compete just to name a few.

At Balance Your Books LLC, we understand that bookkeeping and the paperwork involved in running a business can be stressful and distracting. Our job is to take on those tasks and free up the business owner to focus on what he or she does best-meeting customer needs and growing a successful business.

Our commitment is to perform the tasks entrusted to us with professional skill, integrity and accuracy. The services we provide can be done at our office or at your office location. Our service includes free accounting support when you have questions or get stuck on something. We meet deadlines and make sure your financials and monthly or quarterly tax returns are filed correctly and on time. We take the time to get to know the client, their business and understand what they want and need from us.
